Attributes.description: Clinical practice to integrate and consolidate professional nursing knowledge, skills and competencies in the context of primary health care.
Attributes.prereq: Pre-reqs: All of NURS 300, NURS 310, NURS 321, NURS 322, NURS 330, NURS 352, NURS 360.
Attributes.coreq: Co-reqs: NURS 301 and one of NURS 323, NURS 401.
